text: CFNB may refer to: * CFNB-FM, a radio station (97.5 FM) licensed to D'Arcy, British Columbia, Canada * CIBX-FM, a radio station (106.9 FM) licensed to Fredericton, New Brunswick, Canada, which held the call sign CFNB from 1926 to 1996 A tourist info radio station in Fredericton, New Brunswick Canada
title: CFNB
